OL,6,FThe Infected Blood Inquiry, which was
OL,7,Flaunched in 2017 by former prime
OL,8,Fminister Theresa May, will publish its
OL,9,Ffinal report on Monday.
OL,11,FHundreds of those affected by the
OL,12,Fscandal gathered at Westminster on
OL,13,FSunday afternoon at an event organised
OL,14,Fby the Hepatitis C Trust to mark the
OL,15,Fend of the inquiry.
OL,17,FSome of those in attendance have been
OL,18,Fcampaigning for decades for justice.
