OL,6,FRachel Halford, chief executive of The
OL,7,FHepatitis C Trust, said the fight was
OL,8,Fnot yet over.
OL,10,F"Action from Government to right these
OL,11,Fhistoric wrongs is needed as urgently
OL,12,Fas ever," she said.
OL,14,F"More than 650 who received infected
OL,15,Fblood or blood products have died
OL,16,Fsince the Infected Blood Inquiry began.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/9
