OL,6,F"The Government must implement all the
OL,7,Frecommendations of the inquiry and
OL,8,Fannounce a clear timeline for when
OL,9,Fcompensation payments will be made as
OL,10,Fsoon as possible."
OL,12,FMeanwhile, MP Dame Diana Johnson, who
OL,13,Fhad lobbied on the issue for two
OL,14,Fdecades, spoke of her emotion as she
OL,15,Faddressed the crowd.
OL,17,FShe said: "The journey has been far
OL,18,Ftoo long and far too slow and we know
OL,19,Fthat many are not here when they
OL,20,Fshould be."
