OL,6,FAndy Evans, co-founder of campaign
OL,7,Fgroup Tainted Blood, contracted
OL,8,Fhepatitis C and HIV when he was five
OL,9,Fyears old from being given an infected
OL,10,Fproduct in the 1980s.
OL,12,FHe told the crowd in Westminster:
OL,13,F"We've lost so many people to this
OL,14,Fscandal along the way.
OL,16,F"Many of you are here because you've
OL,17,Flost someone. Our journey to this
OL,18,Fpoint has been defined by loss, and
OL,19,Fhurt, and sadness and by anger.
