OL,6,F"We will never forget all that we've
OL,7,Flost, but with each other's help,
OL,8,Fperhaps now, here, is where we start
OL,9,Fto heal."
OL,11,FFormer soldier Brendan West lost his
OL,12,Fleg in 1979 and was given blood
OL,13,Ftransfusions while at a British
OL,14,Fmilitary hospital in Germany where his
OL,15,Fleg was amputated.
OL,17,FFour decades later, he discovered that
OL,18,Fthe blood he was given was infected
OL,19,Fwith Hepatitis C.
