OL,6,FThe 63-year-old said: "Today is for
OL,7,Fall of those who died and suffered
OL,8,Funnecessarily."
OL,10,FSpeaking ahead of the inquiry, a
OL,11,FGovernment spokesperson said: "This
OL,12,Fwas an appalling tragedy that never
OL,13,Fshould have happened.
OL,15,F"We are clear that justice needs to be
OL,16,Fdone and swiftly, which is why have
OL,17,Facted in amending the Victims and
OL,18,FPrisoners Bill.
