OL,6,F"This includes establishing a new body
OL,7,Fto deliver an Infected Blood
OL,8,FCompensation Scheme, confirming the
OL,9,FGovernment will make the required
OL,10,Fregulations for it within three months
OL,11,Fof Royal Assent, and that it will have
OL,12,Fall the funding needed to deliver
OL,13,Fcompensation once they have identified
OL,14,Fthe victims and assessed claims.
OL,16,F"In addition, we have included a
OL,17,Fstatutory duty to provide additional
OL,18,Finterim payments to the estates of
OL,19,Fdeceased infected people.
